INSERT INTO `recovery_recommendations` VALUES (1,2,2,'SYSTEM FEEDBACK (Fallback Template):\nUser encountered significant friction on the checkout page (Rage Clicks: 31, Errors: 3).\nRecommended Recovery Actions:\n1. Email user with a saved cart link and a 10% apology discount code.\n2. Notify QA team to check checkout form submission logs for ID: payment_submit_btn.\n3. Flag user for customer support outreach if checkout is attempted again.','Pending','2026-06-11 15:45:23'),(2,6,6,'Subject: Personalized Recovery Plan to Address Checkout Friction\n\nDear [User Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I\'m reaching out as the Customer Success AI Specialist because we\'ve noticed that our platform hasn\'t been meeting your expectations during checkout, leading to a high friction score of 86.0/100.\n\nWe\'re committed to resolving this issue and ensuring a seamless experience for you. Based on our analysis, here\'s a customized recovery plan tailored to address the root causes:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: We\'ve identified an average system latency of 131.8 ms as a contributing factor to your frustration. To mitigate this, we\'ll implement a caching solution that reduces server load and minimizes delays during checkout. This change should','Pending','2026-06-11 15:45:32'),(3,10,10,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'re experiencing with our platform. I\'ve reviewed your account, and I\'d like to offer the following personalized recovery plan to help us better meet your needs:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Experience**: We\'ll expedite a review of our checkout process to identify areas causing delays. In the meantime, I recommend using our \"Skip Payment\" option to simplify your transactions.\n\n• **Proactive Error Resolution**: Our team will work closely with you to resolve the errors encountered during your last session (Error Events: 3). We\'ll also provide additional support via [support channel] to ensure a smoother experience.\n\n• **Optimized System Performance**: To minimize latency issues, I recommend using our','Pending','2026-06-11 15:45:40'),(4,14,14,'Hello [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'re experiencing on our platform, which have led to a high Friction Score. I\'ve analyzed your behavior and identified some key areas for improvement. Here are three actionable steps to help you overcome these challenges:\n\n• **Simplified Checkout Process**: We\'ve streamlined our checkout process to reduce errors and increase speed. Please try completing your purchase using the \"Quick Checkout\" option, which skips the address entry step.\n\n• **Error Resolution Assistance**: Our support team is available to help resolve any issues that may arise during the checkout process. If you encounter an error message, please click on the \"Help\" button next to it and follow the prompts to escalate your issue.\n\n• **Reduc','Pending','2026-06-11 15:45:50'),(5,18,18,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m so sorry to hear that you\'re experiencing difficulties on our platform, particularly during the checkout process. Our team has reviewed your account, and we\'d like to offer the following tailored support to help resolve the issues:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Experience**: We\'ll expedite a review of our checkout flow to identify any bottlenecks or areas where we can improve the user experience. In the meantime, I\'ve attached a temporary workaround that should reduce system latency by 50% for your next checkout attempt.\n\n• **Personalized Support**: To better understand your concerns and provide more effective assistance, I\'d like to schedule a personalized call with our dedicated support team. We\'ll work together to address any specific pain points or','Pending','2026-06-11 15:45:57'),(6,20,20,'User Name: [Insert User Name]\n\nDear [User Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out because we\'ve noticed that you\'re experiencing some challenges on our platform, which is why I\'d like to offer the following tailored support:\n\n• **Streamlined Onboarding**: To help you get started more efficiently, I recommend completing your profile and setting up your workflow. This will not only reduce future friction but also provide a better understanding of how our platform can support your work.\n\n• **Error Reduction**: We\'ve noticed that you\'ve encountered 5 errors on our platform recently. Our team is here to help! Please feel free to reach out to us directly so we can investigate and resolve any underlying issues, ensuring a smoother experience moving forward.\n\n• **Performance Optimization**:','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:03'),(7,22,22,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I\'ve been made aware that you\'re experiencing some difficulties on our platform, and I\'m here to help resolve the issues as quickly as possible.\n\nBased on your frustration level and recent activity, I\'ve put together a customized recovery action plan tailored specifically for you:\n\n• **Immediate Resolution**: Our team will expedite the processing of your pending payment, ensuring that any outstanding balances are cleared promptly. This should take effect within the next 24 hours. If you have already made a payment, please allow an additional 2-3 business days for the transaction to be fully processed.\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Experience**: We\'ll provide personalized guidance on optimizing your checkout process. You can expect','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:09'),(8,26,26,'Based on the user\'s details, here is a customized recovery action plan:\n\nDear [User Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'ve been experiencing with our platform. I understand how frustrating it can be when things don\'t go as smoothly as expected.\n\nTo help you get back on track, I\'ve put together a personalized recovery plan:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: We\'ve identified that the average system latency of 121ms may be contributing to your frustration. To alleviate this, we\'re introducing an optimization patch that will reduce checkout loading times by 30%. This should significantly improve the overall user experience.\n\n• **Proactive Error Resolution**: One error event was encountered during your recent visit. Our team is working on resolving the underlying','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:16'),(9,28,28,'Dear [User],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'ve been experiencing on our platform, which has led to a friction score of 30.0/100. I want to assure you that we\'re committed to making your experience better.\n\nBased on your behavior and the data we have, here are three actionable steps I recommend for us to work together to improve your experience:\n\n• **Quick System Check**: Let\'s perform a quick system check to identify any underlying technical issues. Our team will investigate the cause of the average latency of 139.8 ms and ensure that it\'s resolved as soon as possible.\n\n• **Personalized Guidance**: We\'ll provide you with personalized guidance on how to optimize your workflow, including tips on reducing error events','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:22'),(10,30,30,'Dear [User Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'ve been experiencing on our platform, particularly with checkout. Our team has identified some key areas that we\'d like to help resolve for you.\n\nTo get you back on track quickly and efficiently, we recommend the following actions:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: We\'ll expedite a review of your account to optimize your checkout experience. This may involve adjusting any unnecessary fields or simplifying the payment process. Your dedicated support specialist will be in touch with you within 24 hours to discuss these changes.\n\n• **Enhanced Error Reporting**: To minimize future errors, we\'ll provide you with an updated error reporting tool that allows for quicker identification and resolution','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:27'),(11,34,34,'Here\'s a customized recovery action plan for the frustrated user:\n\nDear [User],\n\nI\'m so sorry to hear that you\'re experiencing issues with our platform, particularly during checkout. I want to assure you that we\'re committed to helping you succeed.\n\nAfter reviewing your account activity and performance metrics, I\'ve identified some key areas where we can improve your experience. Please find below a tailored recovery plan to get you back on track:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: We\'ll expedite the review of your payment method to minimize delays and ensure a seamless checkout experience. Our team will also investigate any potential errors or issues that may be causing frustration.\n\n• **Enhanced Error Reporting**: To help us better understand the root cause of the problems you\'re facing,','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:32'),(12,36,36,'Dear [User],\n\nI\'ve reviewed your recent activity on our platform, and I\'m concerned about the friction you\'re experiencing. To help resolve this issue, I\'ve put together a customized recovery plan for you:\n\n• **Optimize System Performance**: Our system latency is currently at 133.8ms, which may be contributing to your frustration. I recommend checking our status page for any known issues and consider reaching out to our support team if the latency persists.\n\n• **Review Error History**: We\'ve encountered five error events during your recent activity. Please take a moment to review these errors and let us know if you\'re able to resolve them on your own or require assistance from our team.\n\n• **Schedule a Support Session**: Given your high friction score','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:38'),(13,38,38,'Hello [User],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'ve been experiencing on our platform. I understand how frustrating it can be, and I want to help resolve these problems as soon as possible.\n\nBased on your recent activity, I\'ve identified some key areas that need attention. Below are three actionable steps to help us get back on track:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: Our team is working to optimize the checkout process, reducing the number of errors and increasing the overall system latency. In the meantime, you can try simplifying your order by removing any unnecessary items or using our pre-filled forms to expedite the process.\n\n• **Error Resolution Support**: We\'ve encountered some technical issues that may be contributing to your frustration. Our support team','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:44'),(14,40,40,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the concerns you\'ve been experiencing with our platform. I understand how frustrating it can be when things don\'t go as expected, and I want to help resolve the issues.\n\nBased on your recent activity, I\'ve identified some areas where we can improve your experience. Here are three actionable steps to get us back on track:\n\n• **Quick Fix:** We\'re going to accelerate our system response time to reduce latency. This will ensure that you can complete tasks efficiently and without interruptions. You\'ll notice an improvement in the next 24 hours.\n\n• **Proactive Support:** Our dedicated support team is here to help. If you encounter any further errors or issues, please don\'t hesitate to reach out','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:49'),(15,42,42,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'re experiencing on our platform, specifically with checkout. I understand how frustrating that can be, and I want to help resolve it for you.\n\nBased on your profile and recent activity, here are three tailored actions we recommend to get you back on track:\n\n• **Streamline Your Checkout Process**: We\'ve identified a potential bottleneck in the payment gateway process. To expedite this, please try updating your payment method or exploring alternative payment options (e.g., credit card or PayPal) to see if that resolves the issue.\n\n• **Verify System Performance**: Our system latency has been slightly above average, which might be contributing to the checkout frustration. We\'re currently investigating and will implement necessary','Pending','2026-06-11 15:46:56'),(16,46,46,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the concerns you\'ve been experiencing with our platform, and I want to assure you that we\'re committed to helping you overcome these challenges.\n\nBased on your recent interactions, I\'ve identified some key areas where we can improve your experience. Here are three actionable steps we recommend:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: We\'ll expedite the checkout process by implementing a simplified payment gateway and reducing the number of form fields required. This will minimize errors and reduce system latency, allowing you to complete your transaction more efficiently.\n\n• **Proactive Error Resolution**: Our team has identified the root cause of the errors you\'ve encountered (3 specific issues). We\'ll proactively resolve these issues through targeted updates, ensuring','Pending','2026-06-11 15:47:01'),(17,50,50,'Hello [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m so sorry to hear that you\'re experiencing issues with our platform, particularly during the checkout process. I\'d like to help resolve these problems as quickly as possible.\n\nBased on your behavior and our system metrics, I\'ve identified some key areas where we can improve your experience:\n\n• **Simplified Checkout Flow**: We\'ll review and optimize our checkout flow to reduce the number of steps required and minimize unnecessary fields for you to fill out. This should help streamline the process and make it more convenient for you.\n\n• **Enhanced Error Messaging**: To prevent further frustration, we\'ll work on improving our error messages to provide clear explanations and actionable next steps. This will enable you to quickly identify and resolve issues on your own','Pending','2026-06-11 15:47:07'),(18,52,52,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'ve been experiencing on our platform, which have led to a friction score of 30.0/100. I want to assure you that we\'re committed to helping you get the most out of our tools.\n\nHere are three actionable steps to help us move forward:\n\n• **Quick System Check**: Please perform a quick system check by clearing your browser cache and cookies, and then try logging in again. This often resolves latency issues and can help resolve errors.\n\n• **Error Reporting**: To better understand the root cause of the issues you\'re facing, could you please provide more context about the 4 error events you\'ve encountered? Your input will help us identify patterns and improve our','Pending','2026-06-11 15:47:12'),(19,54,54,'Dear [User],\n\nI\'ve been notified that you\'re experiencing some difficulties on our platform, and I\'m here to help resolve the issues as soon as possible. Based on your profile and recent activity, I\'ve put together a customized recovery action plan tailored just for you.\n\nHere are three actionable steps to get you back on track:\n\n• **Streamline Your Checkout Process**: We\'ve noticed that there were two error events during your last session. To help you complete the checkout process smoothly, we\'ll provide additional support and guidance. Our dedicated customer success team will be in touch with you within the next 24 hours to review your account settings and ensure everything is up-to-date.\n\n• **Optimize Your System Latency**: We understand that a slow system','Pending','2026-06-11 15:47:17'),(20,58,58,'Dear [User\'s Name],\n\nI\'m reaching out to address the issues you\'re experiencing on our platform, and I want to assure you that we\'re committed to resolving these problems as quickly as possible.\n\nBased on your recent behavior, I\'ve identified some key areas where we can improve your experience. Here are three actionable steps to help us get back on track:\n\n• **Streamlined Checkout Process**: We\'ve noticed that our checkout process has been causing frustration for you, with an average system latency of 112.2 ms and two error events encountered. To mitigate this, I recommend that you review our simplified checkout flow (available in the \"Help\" section) and let us know if there\'s anything we can do to make it more intuitive.\n\n•','Pending','2026-06-11 15:47:27');
